comments: Allen (BKN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Bertan's (WAS) path.
After Bryant (WAS) absorbs the initial body contact, he makes contact with Harris' (BKN)  arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bertans (WAS) and Allen (BKN) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Beal (WAS) brings his hand under the ball and resumes his dribble.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Dinwiddie's (BKN) path.
Dinwiddie (BKN) makes slight contact to the body of Beal (WAS) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Brown Jr. (WAS) delivers contact and dislodges Allen (BKN) during the screen.
As Beal (WAS) comes around the screen, Dinwiddie (BKN) reaches in and grabs his arm causing him to lose control of the ball.
Allen (BKN) and Bryant (WAS) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Dinwiddie (BKN) makes slight contact with Bertans (WAS) on the catch by going to but not through Bertans.
Allen (BKN) makes contact with Beal's (WAS) lower body during the rebound.
Temple (BKN) briefly grasps Brown Jr.'s (WAS) jersey during the rebound.
Dinwiddie (BKN) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
Bonga (WAS) makes marginal contact with Prince's (BKN) arm after making clean contact with the ball during the rebound.
Temple (BKN) reaches in and makes contact with Bonga's (WAS) arm
